---
title: Bacon and Pesto Mac and Peas with Herby Crumb
description: Mac and cheese is a crowd-pleasing American dish with a deliciously cheesy sauce. Here, we're going green by swirling through green pesto and studding with peas and bacon, then topping with a herby crumb for texture and even more flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W22_UK_V17056-6_Main_low-3ac20951.jpg
